parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag module can cause the airbags to deploy unexpectedly or not deploy at all in the event of a crash, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbags deploy unexpectedly
the airbags do not deploy in a crash
the vehicle has been recalled for airbag module replacement.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of recall parts can cause delays in repairing the vehicle, leaving the owner at risk of an airbag deployment or non-deployment in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The dealer is unable to obtain the necessary parts to complete the recall repair
the owner is told to wait for an extended period for the parts to become available.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The incomplete or incorrect repair of the airbag module can cause the airbags to deploy unexpectedly or not deploy at all in the event of a crash, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The dealer fails to replace the correct parts
the repair is not completed correctly
the owner is charged for additional repairs that should be covered under the recall.
